@startuml
participant "Webex Teams" as WebexTeams
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "icanhazdadjoke.com API" as JokeAPI
participant "Webex Teams API" as WebexAPI

WebexTeams -> APIGateway: Webhook request (bot mention)
APIGateway -> Lambda: Invoke Lambda function
activate Lambda

Lambda -> JokeAPI: GET request
JokeAPI --> Lambda: JSON response with joke
Lambda -> Lambda: Parse joke from response

Lambda -> WebexAPI: POST request with joke
WebexAPI --> Lambda: Confirmation

Lambda --> APIGateway: Success message
deactivate Lambda
APIGateway --> WebexTeams: HTTP response
@enduml